
Client to Server

Client will make AJAX calls to WP AJAX interface, sending one of the following commands:
cge_get_user
	Params:
	Return: user : object
cge_get_game_types
	Params:
	Return: list of game types : html
cge_get_joinable_games
	Params:
	Return: ulist of games in progress : html
cge_start_game
	Params: game_type_id : string
	Return: game specification : object
cge_join_game
	Params: game_id : int
	Return: game specification : object
cge_load_deck_spec
	Params: deck_type_id : string
	Return: deck specification : object

Not Yet Implemented:
cge_transaction
	Params: 
		game_id : int
		user_id : int
		from_group_id : string
		to_group_id : string
		items : array of card ids
	Return: transaction_id : int



Server to Client

Server will send Server Sent Events to client, sending on of the following commands:
message (default)
	Params: data : string
	Return: N/A
userJoined
	Params: user : object
	Return: N/A
update
	Params: transaction : object
	Return: N/A

